trans-unit.source: Cancels the manipulation.
trans-unit.target: Avbryter redigeringen.

trans-unit.source: If the method succeeds, the default <xref:System.Windows.Input.TouchDevice> sends previous touch events as mouse down, mouse move, or mouse up events to the element.
trans-unit.target: Hvis metoden lykkes, standard <xref:System.Windows.Input.TouchDevice>sender tidligere touch hendelser som MouseDown, musen Flytt og mus ned hendelser til elementet.</xref:System.Windows.Input.TouchDevice>

trans-unit.source: Touch cannot be promoted to mouse events if the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationCompleted> event occurs during inertia.
trans-unit.target: Berøring kan ikke forfremmes til musen hendelser hvis den <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationCompleted>inntreffer under treghet.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationCompleted>
